> i can see many test data are changed, not sure why.

Changes in `src/sonic-bgpcfgd/tests/data/sonic-cfggen` data dir is due to the change in the sonic-cfggen not returning `natsorted` dict anymore. This causes some entries to change index/order in Python list/dict. The files changed under data directory are used to validate `sonic-cfggen` output and so, the order change of `sonic-cfggen` output required changing those files.

